 company (index 1215): 0.8031\n","Predicted probability of bankruptcy for the non-bankrupt company (index 1244): 0.2384\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["from sklearn.metrics import confusion_matrix\n","\n","# Построение матрицы неточностей\n","cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred)\n","\n","print(\"Матрица неточностей:\")\n","print(cm)\n","\n","# Правильный расчет метрик по матрице [[TN, FP], [FN, TP]]\n","false_positives = cm[0, 1] # Здоровые, названные банкротами\n","false_negatives = cm[1, 0] # Банкроты, названные здоровыми\n","\n","print(f\"\\nКоличество ложно определенных банкротов (False Positive): {false_positives}\")\n","print(f\"Количество пропущенных банкротов (False Negative): {false_negatives}\")"],"metadata":{"id":"Q4a0Vik2NpMD","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780569514989,"user_tz":-300,"elapsed":73,"user":{"displayName":"Ta Sha","userId":"13567804846267301364"}},"outputId":"20e74d45-4c19-464f-9e67-fb8bc449a66d","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"}},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Матрица неточностей:\n","[[1142  178]\n"," [   5   39]]\n","\n","Количество ложно определенных банкротов (False Positive): 178\n","Количество пропущенных банкротов (False Negative): 5\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsClassifier\n","import pandas as pd\n","\n","# 1. Задаем тот же самый набор факторов (признаков), что просили в методичке\n","features_knn = [\n","    ' ROA(C) before interest and depreciation before interest',\n","    ' ROA(A) before interest and % after tax',\n","    ' ROA(B) before interest and depreciation after tax',\n","    ' Operating Gross Margin', ' Realized Sales Gross Margin',\n","    ' Operating Profit Rate', ' Pre-tax net Interest Rate',\n","    ' After-tax net Interest Rate', ' Non-industry income and expenditure/revenue',\n","    ' Net Income to Total Assets', ' Total assets to GNP price'\n","]\n","\n","# Ограничиваем наши выборки только этими признаками\n","X_train_knn = X_train[features_knn]\n","X_test_knn = X_test[features_knn]\n","\n","# 2. Обучаем модель kNN (зададим стандартное число соседей k=5)\n","knn_model = KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=5)\n","knn_model.fit(X_train_knn, y_train)\n","\n","# Делаем прогноз на тестовой выборке\n","y_pred_knn = knn_model.predict(X_test_knn)\n","\n","# 3. Строим аналог CrossTable из R с помощью pd.crosstab в Python\n","print(\"--- Таблица сопряженности (CrossTable) ---\")\n","cross_table = pd.crosstab(y_test, y_pred_knn, rownames=['Actual'], colnames=['Predicted'], margins=True)\n","print(cross_table)\n","\n","# 4. Находим количество ложно определенных банкротов для kNN\n","# В матрице [[TN, FP], [FN, TP]] ложно определенные банкроты (FP) — это cross_table.at[0, 1]\n","# Но для надежности посчитаем их напрямую через сравнение массивов:\n","falsely_identified_knn = ((y_test == 0) & (y_pred_knn == 1)).sum()\n","\n","print(\"\\n--- Результаты анализа kNN ---\")\n","print(f\"Количество ложно определенных банкротов для метода kNN: {falsely_identified_knn}\")"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"QDvwGZPERkZe","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780571129950,"user_tz":-300,"elapsed":409,"user":{"displayName":"Ta Sha","userId":"13567804846267301364"}},"outputId":"023ea4a4-ea48-455c-fbd6-244b4befd062"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["--- Таблица сопряженности (CrossTable) ---\n","Predicted     0   1   All\n","Actual                   \n","0          1312   8  1320\n","1            41   3    44\n","All        1353  11  1364\n","\n","--- Результаты анализа kNN ---\n","Количество ложно определенных банкротов для метода kNN: 8\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":209},"id":"19731d42","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780570713572,"user_tz":-300,"elapsed":1175,"user":{"displayName":"Ta Sha","userId":"13567804846267301364"}},"outputId":"b86198bf-a8b2-44b0-80ec-d9625cc4e407"},"source":["import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n","from sklearn.metrics import roc_curve, auc\n","\n","# Calculate ROC curve and AUC for Logistic Regression\n","fpr_lr, tpr_lr, _ = roc_curve(y_test, y_proba)\n","roc_auc_lr = auc(fpr_lr, tpr_lr)\n","\n","# Calculate ROC curve and AUC for kNN\n","# We need probabilities for kNN, not just predictions\n","y_proba_knn = knn_model.predict_proba(X_test_knn)[:, 1]\n","fpr_knn, tpr_knn, _ = roc_curve(y_test, y_proba_knn)\n","roc_auc_knn = auc(fpr_knn, tpr_knn)\n","\n","# Plot ROC curves\n","plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))\n","plt.plot(fpr_lr, tpr_lr, color='darkorange', lw=2, label=f'Logistic Regression (AUC = {roc_auc_lr:.2f})')\n","plt.plot(fpr_knn, tpr_knn, color='green', lw=2, label=f'kNN (AUC = {roc_auc_knn:.2f})')\n","plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1], color='navy', lw=2, linestyle='--', label='Random Classifier')\n","plt.xlim([0.0, 1.0])\n","plt.ylim([0.0, 1.05])\n","plt.xlabel('False Positive Rate')\n","plt.ylabel('True Positive Rate')\n","plt.title('Receiver Operating Characteristic (ROC) Curve Comparison')\n","plt.legend(loc='lower right')\n","plt.grid(True)\n","plt.show()"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 1000x800 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]}]}